      "description": "The First Trust International Rising Dividend Achievers ETF (IDVY) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in total market equity. The fund tracks an index comprised of developed-market firms outside the US that have demonstrated rising dividends and earnings growth. The fund aims to provide broad international equity exposure weighted by fundamental factors. IDVY was launched on Feb 10, 2026 and is issued by First Trust.",
